<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4802&amp;p=42528#p42528"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[What could cause my background to not show up at all?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=4802&amp;p=42528#p42528"><![CDATA[
If you open FCEUXD or any emulator with a name table viewer, check if the tiles are on the name table. If they are, then it's either that the scroll isn't set correctly or that you forgot to enable the background in $2001. If they aren't on the name table, there's a problem when you try and write to the name table. Hope this helps.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=138">Celius</a> — Thu Jan 29, 2009 9:48 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
